The '''''Nordieus''''' was a civilian [[Transport/Legends|transport]] [[Starship/Legends|ship]]. The ship was used by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] to transport [[Atour Riten]] and several other contractors to the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|DS-1 Orbital Battle Station]] while it was under construction at [[Despayre]].

